  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-22ee17d5-165a-467b-b0eb-3c81ba595a25\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-059e7b0e-a8b8-478b-bbc3-8118d797a035\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e2571-9142-11ed-86ed-4f41cdd2c537\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 + 인스타그램</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5113cbf-c95d-46c3-b7b8-81c99230fa22\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e2572-9142-11ed-86ed-137b5ac299fd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">오늘은 요즘 가장 많이 활용되는 인스타그램용 사이즈로 작업된 업그레이드 버전을 소개합니다. 지금까지 프로필명함은 종이의 가로사이즈와는 달리 세로로 길게 만들어지고 모바일에서 이미지를 열었을 때 최적화된 사이즈라고 설명드렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cef5500e-dbe5-4566-90ad-6774c02dff3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e2573-9142-11ed-86ed-b948dfa7bdf9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a112724a-7f42-4942-83ed-051506e80a99\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-111b63d2-29b3-4fb0-8e1f-6768bc832fc5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c84-9142-11ed-86ed-05fb4eb57fa6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">하지만 이 모바일용사이즈는 요즘 이미지앱의 최애 프로그램인 인스타그램용과는 다소 맞지 않는 경향이 있습니다. 아래는 정무늬대표님 프로필명함 이미지가 인스타그램에 들어 갔을 때의 모습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce754c1c-f2a2-47b2-a758-f3cb82df2439\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:872px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18d4a7a1-9219-48ff-9c7a-61a2beb628ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f76d573-6430-4dd7-943f-8bafe29a1c7b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c85-9142-11ed-86ed-4f0b5fab971f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">보시는 것과 같이 인스타그램의 메인사이즈는 정사각형입니다. 이로 인해서 긴 핸드폰사이즈와는 맞지 않는 부분이 있습니다. 이를 수정하기 위해 인스타그램용 이미지 사이즈로의 변형이 불가피했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-c0ba98f2-77fa-4d70-8f0a-b20263e6386b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2acdf669-d7b4-4911-b018-65284411ddaf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b915c78-07f9-412a-8928-c109f539b280\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c86-9142-11ed-86ed-a3fc7c14d097\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 + 인스타그램</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-32572ccc-c1a4-4b1a-89d3-d0198f7d8933\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fed41276-6567-438d-b335-060aa813b36b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-695e4c87-9142-11ed-86ed-ebcb0842a08c\" style=\"\">인스타그램용 정사각형</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ed2d8c6d-59fc-4ccf-b24a-ac79ed9fdeae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-729d97a6-3634-46bc-ba78-62c638f160ec\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c88-9142-11ed-86ed-65b86b386424\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-398bb0bd-bd7f-4e01-9492-c3264a154336\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bf12113-c876-4c3e-9c1e-bfa672c4a4a1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c89-9142-11ed-86ed-91d3cb8725e1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함의 활용도는 무한합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a90e9354-4fe0-4c97-a28a-dbb33ea2f173\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c8a-9142-11ed-86ed-39389a5ad61d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프로필명함을 하나 만들어 놓으면 영상까지 제작할 수 있고 또한 인스타그램용 이미지로까지의 변환을 가장 저렴한 금액으로 제작하실 수 있습니다. 이는 우리가 흔하 말하는 3박자 (종이명함 + 모바일명함 + 인스타그램이미지)를 모두 충족할 수 있다는 의미입니다. 거기에 영상까지 제작이 가능하니 덤을 받으신 느낌이 드실겁니다. 이처럼 프로필명함은 활용도가 높으며 가장 효율적인 명함으로의 작업이 되실 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fb1a72d5-fe46-4b71-9c36-521f56f86eb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47080201-91cf-4279-9b6b-a6ee6085f3ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-695e4c8b-9142-11ed-86ed-d7e5f43bfb76\" style=\"\">종이명함</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f59f318-95d0-4e6a-8c39-0849f8655b87\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a998ca9e-9b9f-481d-a44c-d30a7096184d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-695e4c8c-9142-11ed-86ed-a1830f1135db\" style=\"\">프로필명함</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c926668-76ac-47de-9b1a-78ca3b36061e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba4c1646-fae7-495c-b778-4bed2047cc1e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-695e4c8d-9142-11ed-86ed-2fd950992723\" style=\"\">인스타용 이미지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-97e34f88-9e73-4345-9c48-fae69edf5dae\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aa53ac8a-8e8b-49f6-b3dd-db4c1d7c9fbc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-8c991085-0f48-4e86-a407-7f85e2be1d77\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e043dfc-87c8-42d0-ba22-94122270d94f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c8e-9142-11ed-86ed-d58df91bd0c2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필명함 이미지는 이렇게 관리하세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90a1bfc1-4a23-488e-be48-fc0edcee69c5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c8f-9142-11ed-86ed-f929b26fc00e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프로필명함은 이미지입니다. png파일이기 때문에 디지털 형태로 제출되며 최종 결과물 또한 디지털 이미지입니다. 종이명함과는 달리 하드웨어적인 물질이 아니기 때문에 쉽게 잊어 버리고 손실되는 경우가 있습니다.특히 이 결과물은 모바일로 많이 보관하고 계시고 이미지이다 보니 찾거나 검색이 자주 발생될 수 있어서 카카오톡의 톡서랍의 중요 기능을 이용해서 보관해 놓으시길 추천드립니다. 또한 개인 pc나 구글박스에 올려놓으셔도 좋습니다.  다음은 카카오톡에서의 보관 방법을 영상으로 올려봅니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c90-9142-11ed-86ed-7d5b60533e72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31207dc8-9896-46c1-b28c-6d53d9733f57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e4c91-9142-11ed-86ed-1d87f1062a54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" style=\"max-width:334px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-5d92758a-de42-43b9-ba55-f9b2a098bfb0\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0921990b-8f8f-4897-bae5-a6b5fd713ede\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77af2876-b49d-4e75-aa52-9420e44fa271\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a2-9142-11ed-86ed-a7b903f330fd\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">톡서랍에서 이미지를 빨리 검색해서 찾고 보관하는 방법입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7172a41b-52dc-4b3e-90a0-4bb6d3a8e3f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/007.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f8f89735-7f91-4247-ba65-3fd5ed0ad397\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-caaad3a3-269a-4cd1-978f-d763fb83c335\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a3-9142-11ed-86ed-1b50a5683ba0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지를 (주)파파스컴퍼니에서 받으시면 이렇게 png파일로 받으실 겁니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a4-9142-11ed-86ed-a7edf985b96a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42ad3c38-2a4f-4682-9983-a3252d3ff074\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a5-9142-11ed-86ed-5396bbcf38e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e2f1208f-1a3c-4aa6-92de-d1860f5c55f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72ada312-fa45-470b-9252-f8cb75ef8ba7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-805c77c0-2327-4d59-b640-ee21c84daf18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a6-9142-11ed-86ed-b74d223b010f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이때 위에 마킹하는 부분이 있습니다. 이 부분을 마킹해 놓으시면 중요이미지로 구분이 됩니다. 이미지와 드린 동영상까지 모두 가능합니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니에서 드린 이미지와 동영상까지 모두 마킹처리를 해 놓으시길 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4fac7044-9144-4d74-9511-9442eff08203\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b503f666-47bc-458a-aaf7-9d5e0010346a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22a22b16-c8d2-44bb-9e15-a9606ab84ef1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a7-9142-11ed-86ed-c3a3398d0dde\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">맨 상단에 톡서랍 기능을 오픈하시면 중요이미지는 따로 보실 수 있습니다. 톡으로 받은 모든 이미지는 보관이 되지만 그 이미지를 찾는 건 매우 어려운 일입니다. 이때 (주)파파스컴퍼니에서 받으신 영상과 이미지를 중요이미지로 분리해 놓으세요. 그러면 간단하게 필요할 때 찾으실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb4a166c-4eb3-41b1-8e5a-8998805f1829\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b551125-9389-43e9-a4ab-7f87079f9a14\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222980038699/011.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-515c4fc1-e327-453c-8e32-5ee711905da1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-389f896c-33a5-45c2-83f1-864908e2d107\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a8-9142-11ed-86ed-ab9d74c3565e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이렇게 중요 이미지만 따로 보고 관리할 수 있습니다. 이건 빨리 이미지나 영상을 찾을 수 있다는 뜻입니다. 잘 보간하시고 잘 활용해 주시면 좋겠습니다.~</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73a9-9142-11ed-86ed-3f60cea6b2a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66f5b810-b3df-41ff-a115-ef26a4d9a5f7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-695e73aa-9142-11ed-86ed-e9c9eb29eb6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1184f5ab-59f6-4e5b-b537-4bb3d5bb8f71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}